### Educational Use

This software is designed for educational purposes in MBA, CFA, and FRM programs.
It demonstrates advanced financial modeling concepts and best practices in quantitative finance.

### Disclaimer

This tool is provided for educational and analytical purposes only.
It is NOT financial advice. Users must conduct their own due diligence and consult
with financial advisors before making investment decisions.

